{
  "stem": "1603.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he said, taken-- we're going to be taken away, probably to Germany or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't remember if he said that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't recall that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he just said 'be taken away' and I think it meant to us a death camp kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I spoke with him at age 14.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I spoke with my father for five minutes before he was taken away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] [SOB] I wish that there going to be no kid in this universe who will have to experience anything like that ever-- ever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] going back where we lived, close to the end of the war we were liberated there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were liberated there by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and then what we heard is that my father is alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He's on his way home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he never came home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He never came home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] for many years, quite frequently I would have dreams that-- that my father arrived home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would be crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would say, Father, that is fantastic you are home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the next time when I would have this dream, I would talk to him about the dream I had before that he came home.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, isn't it interesting that I had a dream that you came home?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was an endless, endless motion picture, so to speak, where I had these dreams after dreams.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] probably-- probably all this and more what I saw, which is just a little part I was telling, because I saw many things during World War II and experienced things, which I have no immediate recollection.",
      "word_count": 41
    }
  ],
